##Requires: gsl libraries (>1.14) include files in CPPFLAGS or default include
##location. Also gsl and gslcblas libraries in LDFLAGS or default library location.
##
##For example: If gsl is installed in the location denoted by variable GSL_LOC,
##then run the install.sh as follows:
##CPPFLAGS=-I$GSL_LOC/include LDFLAGS=-L$GSL_LOC/lib ./install.sh

## If gsl is in one of the default locations, run as follows
# ./install.sh

